<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA96">
<l>tiṟampāteṉ ṉeñcamē ceṅkaṇmāl kaṇṭā</l>
<l>yaṟampāva meṉṟiraṇṭu māvāṉ – puṟantāṉim</l>
<l>maṇṭāṉ maṟikaṭaṟāṉ mārutantāṉ vāṉṟāṉē</l>
<l>kaṇṭāy kaṭaikkaṭ piṭi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, unswervingly see red-eyed Māl.</l>
<l>He is both merit and evil. He is outside,</l>
<l>this earth, the churning sea, the wind, the sky is he,</l>
<l>see, [he is] a hold at the end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
